Name: Dodge Dancer
About the game: Overview Enjoy some sweet chiptunes while you dodge frantically about a 3x3 grid. Get a perfect score, and unlock added difficulty modifiers for an extra challenge. Keep Dodge Dude from getting hit 10 times, and he'll smile because you're good at the game. 8 songs 5 difficulty modifiers Challenging tracks A whole lot of fun Get in there and see that smiling pixel man face.
